dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係搵極都冇啲黃嘅經紀，真心唔想比啲藍絲仆街賺傭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"睇幾次樓好難分。賣樓俾你果個都可能係藍，大agent 全部公司都藍。<br />\n<br />\n咁不如唔揾AA直接deal，但你好難分。除非好似上次我去睇樓咁果個業主有埋之前蘋果本野喺書房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以都係focus 翻最基本個消費先。"},{"pid":"1e2e5a8be7fcac195007920fca86c1cbae0a20e6","tid":2000691,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0db744d9568cf95585cc769c4f5ca679b7d56a0f","tid":2000691,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"黃嘅保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1c4681cadb41648baf12cf3739589c417f5016","tid":2000691,"uid":97314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9827e0451d493168facccbd5294b164d88348b2a","tid":2000691,"uid":10509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"同佢簽約之前要求佢大叫  <br />\n光復香港 黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"響警局門口嗌"},{"pid":"4adcebfced6a5f635a5694c66d3b1b20250d5254","tid":2000691,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}